Talks</span><br></h1></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" id="r-1596980964958" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1596980964958" style="float: none; margin: auto; display: block;" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="12" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1596783587877" data-id="1596783587877"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1596980964998" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1596980964998"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 670px !important; height: 156.734px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 335px 78.3672px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 670px !important; height: 156.734px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="65" height="21" style="display: none; top: 68px !important; left: 44px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-679023" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><div>Hey there SkinTalks&nbsp;readers! We totally get it if you've struggled with dry skin and all the annoyances that come with it - <span style="background-color: rgb(253, 244, 236);">the flakiness, the tightness, and that overall lackluster look</span>. But don't worry, because we're here to help! We've got a bunch of affordable skincare options that can give your skin the nourishment and moisture it craves, without breaking the bank.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>In this SkinTalks blog, we're going to walk you through a simple <span style="font-weight: bold;">five-step dry skin routine</span> that works wonders. Plus, we'll be sharing some of our absolute favourite products for dry skin. So, let's dive in and get that hydrated complexion your skin has been dreaming of!</div></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" id="r-1681731921397" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1681731921397" style="float: none; margin: auto; display: block;" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1596783587877" data-id="1596783587877"><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1681731921345" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1681731921345" data-layout-lg="8+4" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="8+4" data-layout-sm="8+4" data-layout-xs="12+12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-8 gf_col-md-8 gf_col-sm-8 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653642484175" data-id="1653642484175"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1681731921352" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1681731921352"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 25px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 12.5px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 26px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-5051" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">1. Pyunkang Yul - Essence Toner&nbsp;</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1681731921395" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1681731921395" style=""><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 313.469px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 156.734px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 313px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="58" height="21" style="display: none; top: 46px !important; left: 115px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-91640" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" data-exc=""><p><br></p><p>Let's talk about toners! Toners are used for various reasons in skin care. They prep the skin for your next skin care step and <span style="background-color: rgb(253, 244, 236);">help to restore the skin's natural pH balance</span>.</p><p><br></p><p>The Pyunkang Yul <a href="https://koreanskincare.nl/products/pyunkang-yul-essence-toner?variant=32521199878207" class="" style="text-decoration: underline;" data-position="1">Essence Toner</a> has become one of the most beloved products in the K-Beauty community. It has a minimalist ingredient list, is <span style="background-color: rgb(253, 244, 236);">free of any extra fragrance</span> and adds a punch of hydration to the skin.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>On a deeper note the formulation itself not only provides hydration, but also promotes texture improvement, antioxidant benefits, and soothing properties. It is no surprise that it is also one of our best-selling products.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1681731921306" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1681731921306"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 313.469px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 156.734px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 313px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="58" height="21" style="display: none; top: 46px !important; left: 115px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-91640" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" data-exc=""><p><br></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 gf_col-md-4 gf_col-sm-4 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1680167576362" data-id="1680167576362"><div data-label="Product" data-key="product" data-atomgroup="product" id="m-1681731921357" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-product" data-ver="3.1" data-id="1681731921357" data-assigned-ver="4" style="min-height: auto;"><div class="module" data-variant="33188526882879" data-current-variant="32521199878207" style="">{% assign product = all_products['pyunkang-yul-essence-toner'] %}{% unless product.empty?  %}{% form 'product', product, id: "", class: "AddToCartForm ", data-productid: product.id %}<input name="id" type="hidden" value="{{product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id}}" data-productid="{{product.id}}"><div data-index="1" class="item-content"><div class="module-wrap" id="m